                     <interp inst="t18420822-2330-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp> for feloniously forging and uttering an acquittance and receipt for 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., on the <rs id="t18420822-cd-156" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420822-2330-offence-1 t18420822-cd-156"></join>14th of June</rs>, with intent to defraud <persName id="t18420822-name-803" type="victimName">
