                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420822-2330-offence-1 t18420822-name-803"></join>Charlotte Pegrim</persName>.—Two other <hi rend="smallCaps">COUNTS</hi>, stating his intent to be to defraud <persName id="t18420822-name-804" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18420822-name-804" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420822-name-804" type="surname" value="CEAL"></interp>
